Jeremiah 31-23 <pb/>Thus says the LORD of hosts, the God of Israel: “Once more they shall use these words in the land of Judah and in its cities, <f>ⓔ</f>when I restore their fortunes: <pb/><t><f>ⓕ</f>“‘The LORD bless you, <f>ⓖ</f>O habitation of righteousness, </t><t><f>ⓗ</f>O holy hill!’ </t>
